name: Wooden Push Duck Toy - Dexter
description:
Wooden Push Ducks are a classic, fun and treasured toy. 

Dexter is the classic patriarch duck featuring a forest green head and a golden bill. His "feathers" are a distinguished textured deep brown created from a top quality vinyl. 

Dexter loves to waddle (or strut) around the lake with his infamous slapping sound "webbed feet". With a large wooden knob for easy grasping, this is a wonderful push toy to accompany those first steps!


Dimensions: 11"L x 6"W x 28"H
